<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8308693>
    dc:description "FIGURE 66. Species of Urginavia Speta displayed in horizontal rows of images. 1. Urginavia kniphofioides (Baker) Mart.-Azorín et al. (Photographs by D. Oosthuizen); 2. Urginavia multisetosa (Baker) Mart.-Azorín et al.; 3. Urginavia simensis (Hochst. ex A.Rich.) Mart.- Azorín et al. (Photographs by B. Stedje)." ;
